CONSENT IN ROLEPLAY

AetherMUD supports mature themes in a post-apocalyptic setting. All players
should respect boundaries:

  - Stop if another player asks you to stop OOC.
  - Do not force capture, torture, or sexual scenes without agreement.
  - Use OOC to clarify boundaries before intense scenes.

Staff may intervene when consent is clearly violated or when content
crosses into harassment under help harassment.

